@startuml sequence
' --- estilo moderno 2026 (flat, redondeado, paleta del proyecto; fondo claro para legibilidad en GitHub) ---
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 12
skinparam DefaultFontColor #0F172A
skinparam DefaultFontSize 13
skinparam ArrowColor #64748B
skinparam ArrowFontColor #475569
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam classBorderColor #0891B2
skinparam classBorderThickness 1.1
skinparam classAttributeFontColor #334155
skinparam stateBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam stateBorderColor #0891B2
skinparam usecaseBackgroundColor #ECFEFF
skinparam usecaseBorderColor #0891B2
skinparam actorBackgroundColor #FFEDD5
skinparam actorBorderColor #C2410C
skinparam packageBackgroundColor #F1F5F9
skinparam packageBorderColor #94A3B8
skinparam componentBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam componentBorderColor #0891B2
skinparam nodeBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam nodeBorderColor #475569
skinparam participantBackgroundColor #F1F5F9
skinparam participantBorderColor #94A3B8
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #CBD5E1
skinparam sequenceGroupBackgroundColor #F1F5F9
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FEF9C3
skinparam noteBorderColor #CA8A04
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam activityBorderColor #0891B2
skinparam activityDiamondBackgroundColor #FFEDD5
skinparam activityDiamondBorderColor #C2410C
skinparam objectBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
skinparam objectBorderColor #0891B2
' Diagrama de secuencia (UML) — configuracion, bucle de control y monitoreo.
title Que hace el sistema

actor "Usuario (admin)" as U
participant "Frontend React" as FE
participant "Backend\nSpring Boot" as API
database "MongoDB" as DB
participant "Raspberry\n(Python + DHT)" as RPi
participant "Relay + Cooler" as HW

== 1) Configuracion de umbrales (con auditoria) ==
U -> FE : Define tempMin/Max, humMin/Max, histeresis, intervalo
FE -> API : POST /api/config
API -> DB : Guarda config activa (quien, email, cuando, IP)
API --> FE : 201 Created

== 2) Bucle de control en la Raspberry ==
loop cada measurementIntervalSeconds
  RPi -> API : GET /api/config/latest
  API --> RPi : Umbrales + histeresis + intervalo
  RPi -> RPi : Lee sensor DHT (temperatura, humedad)
  alt supera umbral (aplicando histeresis)
    RPi -> HW : Enciende cooler (relay ON)
  else dentro de rango
    RPi -> HW : Apaga cooler (relay OFF)
  end
  RPi -> API : POST /api/measurements (temp, hum, coolerOn, status)
  API -> DB : Persiste la medicion (historial)
end

== 3) Monitoreo y auditoria ==
U -> FE : Abre dashboard / historial
FE -> API : GET /api/measurements, /api/config/history
API -> DB : Consulta
API --> FE : Datos
FE --> U : Estado actual, graficos e historial
@enduml
